<kml>

<concept name=Support>
<superconcept name=Obstruct>

<hr>
<h3>Component Semantics:</h3>
<component tag=Support>
  <definition>prevent from falling</definition>
  <requiredslot name=object>
    <restriction>a Tangible-Entity</restriction>
  </requiredslot>
  <requiredslot name=post-conditions>
    <restriction><slot>object</slot> is the <slot>object</slot> of a
      <conceptref name=Be-Supported></restriction>
  </requiredslot>
  <primaryslot name=agent>
    <inheritedfrom name=Obstruct>
    <restriction>causes <slot>object</slot> to be supported</restriction>
  </primaryslot>
  <primaryslot name=instrument>
    <inheritedfrom name=Obstruct>
    <restriction>used to support <slot>object</slot></restriction>
    <restriction>the "support"</restriction>
  </primaryslot>
  <wnsynsets><verb>support#4
  </verb></wnsynsets>
  <wnsynsets><verb>hold#16, hold_up#1, sustain#5
  </verb></wnsynsets>
</component>

<musing>
Support puts an <slot>object</slot> into a 
<conceptref name=Be-Supported> state, which prevents the <slot>object</slot>
from being the <slot>object</slot> of a <conceptref name=Fall> action.
<conceptref name=Let-Fall> takes the <slot>object</slot> out of the
<conceptref name=Be-Supported> state.
</musing>

