<reference source=Levin>
Levin has much to say about <langelement>Support</langelement>, the
<term>positive admire-type psych verb</term> but not much about 
physical support. The one mention of physical support is in Part Two
where it appears among <term>verbs of contiguous location</term>.
The requirement that <slot>agent</slot> and <slot>object</slot> be
contiguous is true of all <conceptref name=Obstruct> Actions.
</reference>

